      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;-googles-new-ai-strategy-pay-engineers-to-do-absolutely-nothing-&#34;&gt;💼 Google’s New AI Strategy: Pay Engineers to Do&amp;hellip; Absolutely Nothing 😴💸&lt;a href=&#34;#-googles-new-ai-strategy-pay-engineers-to-do-absolutely-nothing-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You’ve heard of quiet quitting. Now get ready for &lt;strong&gt;quiet retaining&lt;/strong&gt; — Google-style. 😂&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;-whats-going-on&#34;&gt;🧠 What’s Going On?&lt;a href=&#34;#-whats-going-on&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;According to reports, &lt;strong&gt;Google is paying some AI employees to literally do nothing for a year&lt;/strong&gt; rather than risk them getting scooped up by the competition.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
